NAME
     rev - reverse the characters on each line of a file

SYNOPSIS
     rev [file] ...

EXAMPLES

     rev file            # Reverse each line

DESCRIPTION

     Each file is copied to standard output with all the  characters  of  each
     line reversed, last one first and first one last.

SEE ALSO
     rev(1).



































